title: 465. Introducing a New “Freakonomics of Medicine” Podcast
description: Bapu Jena was already a double threat: a doctor who’s also an economist. Now he’s a podcast host too. In this sneak preview of the Freakonomics Radio Network’s newest show, Bapu discovers that marathons can be deadly — but not for the reasons you may think.
author: editor@freakonomics.com (Freakonomics Radio + Stitcher)
